metadata.name: GOATNET OG FOUNDERS CRDNTL
metadata.description: GOATNET CRDNTL is an NFT that offers membership to GOATNET, a greatness themed movement and Web3 entertainment enterprise. Holders receive a subscription to GOATNET's streaming platform at no additional cost, a front row seat to invest in Goat Studios projects, as well as valuable IRL utility including discounted attendance to Goatfest regional events attended by Goats and featuring the best of sports, music, gaming, culinary, fashion, and more.
